      {
        "id": 7,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 8,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "Approach",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "End of Act 2:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "After overcoming the trials and challenges of the previous section, the Villain faces their greatest challenge yet. This is the moment they have been waiting for throughout the story, as they prepare to use their devastating weapon, launch their armies, ready their final trap, or otherwise enact their diabolical plan. Only one obstacle remains... the Hero."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Show the Villain's preparations coming close to fruition."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Create a sense of possibility that the Villain will be successful in their plan."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Bring the Villain to the cusp of success before the Hero comes in to ruin their fun."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Create a dramatic and thrilling final showdown – this is the major confrontation of the story."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 2 makes up 50% of the story from 25% - 75%."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Approach occurs around the 55% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
