      {
        "id": 6,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 7,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "Test, Allies, and Enemies",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Middle of Act 2:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Villain faces a series of tests and challenges, often failing again and again – don't forget, there is a pesky Hero trying to foil their plans! Whether they're seeking a lost item, tracking down the Hero, hunting those that betrayed them, or seeking new information, these challenges block the Villain's path; so, the Villain seeks Allies to assist them in achieving their ultimate goal. At some point, the Villain is offered a chance at salvation, an opportunity to turn back from their chosen path, but they refuse."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Have the Villain face a series of challenges, each offering a lesson and leading directly to the next challenge. "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Create empathy for the Villain and show things from their perspective."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Introduce Allies to assist the Villain in facing their obstacles – some of whom may perish, quit the adventure, or be sacrificed by the Villain for the cause."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Create exciting and interesting ways for the Villain to fail."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Offer the Villain some form of victory, which helps lead them to their largest challenge."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 2 makes up 50% of the story from 25% - 75%."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Tests, Allies, and Enemies occurs around the 35% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
