      {
        "id": 5,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 6,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "Crossing the Threshold",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Beginning of Act 2:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Villain officially Crosses the Threshold by taking action and committing a serious offence or crime. They may steal, kill, rob, or kidnap, but whatever it is, they are now past the point of no return and are beginning on the path to their ultimate goal. They are now unquestionably the story's Villain."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Re-establish the Central Issue of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "What action does the Villain take to push them beyond the point of return?"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "How do these actions further the Villain's diabolical schemes?"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 2 makes up 50% of the story from 25% - 75%."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Crossing the Threshold occurs around the 25% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
