      {
        "id": 4,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 5,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "Meeting the Mentor",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "End of Act 1:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Villain's Mentor may be a more powerful Villain, a figure of command, or another form of assistance: an object of power; a book; or access to dangerous information. The knowledge, skills, or objects they gain will assist them on their Journey. The Mentor helps the Villain feel prepared enough to begin."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Introduce the Villain's Mentor or guiding force."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Identify the knowledge, tools, or other forms of support provided by the Mentor."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Show how the Mentor works with the Villain to change their perspective."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Demonstrate how the new knowledge or abilities can assist the Villain in their mission."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 1 makes up the first 25% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Meeting the Mentor occurs around the 20% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
