      {
        "id": 3,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 4,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "Refusal of the Call",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Middle of Act 1:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Villain may not be willing to jump at the Call to Adventure immediately: they may hesitate or refuse to kill someone, attempt to find another solution to their problem, or rationalize the event which upset their world. By contrast, a willing Villain will be ready to jump into the action but may be prevented by obstacles that first need to be overcome."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Have the Villain hesitate or refuse the call – perhaps include a twinge of conscience (e.g. hesitating to take action against an old friend or ally)."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Present the Villain's counterarguments to taking up the challenge."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Raise the stakes so that the Villain ultimately has no choice but to act."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 1 makes up the first 25% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Refusal of the Call occurs around the 15% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
