      {
        "id": 1,
        "lineId": 1,
        "beatId": 2,
        "bookId": null,
        "positionWithinLine": 0,
        "positionInBeat": 0,
        "title": "Ordinary World",
        "description": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "--- Add Your Details Above this Line ---"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Beginning of Act 1:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "As the story begins, the Villain is in their Ordinary World... and something is not quite right. For example: an important project they've been working on has gone wrong; they feel betrayed by their government; they've witnessed a loved one die; or they've given in to their darkest desires. This section either creates sympathy for the Villain or a feeling of revulsion. Either way, the key is to hook the reader with an emotional response to the Villain's behavior."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Introduce the readers to the Villain and their Ordinary World."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Show something in the Villain's world that displeases them."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 1 makes up the first 25% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Ordinary World brings the story to about the 10% mark."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
